      <title>沃尔玛出售股权致京东领跌中国科技股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/chinese-tech-stocks-under-pressure-as-walmart-plans-jd-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔玛公司计划出售其在京东公司的股份，且主要参与者的盈利不佳，导致中国消费前景令人担忧，中国科技股暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/chinese-tech-stocks-under-pressure-as-walmart-plans-jd-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:07:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
